            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[感冒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_ganmao-286fc59b6d.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E4%B8%8E%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%A0%E5%8A%A0%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E4%B8%8E%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%A0%E5%8A%A0%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#甲流与新冠有可能叠加感染吗#</span></a>？】当前是流感流行季节。专家介绍，在身体免疫功能低下、新冠病毒还没完全清除的情况下，如果防护不到位，会有同时感染的可能性。得过甲流后，短时间内会形成一定的免疫屏障，“今年感染甲流，明年若再感染症状可能不重或没症状。”<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#预防甲流要注意什么#</span></a>？专家解读👇🏻 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4879198700109908" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hbzdj6qy9lj60rp0flk0802.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/gmiqovHWlx083Rudp6Yo01041200rvT60E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BVp4ysnknHVZu&amp;Expires=1678944055&amp;ssig=iBYIKTYaYE&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/dEQ0uReelx083RucM2Y801041200eLUw0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BVp4ysnknHVZu&amp;Expires=1678944055&amp;ssig=WFab4AT%2FqY&amp;KID=unistore,video"><sou